---
// No client-side interactivity needed for this component
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import referralImage from '../assets/i8fun-referral.webp';
---

<section class="w-full bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    {/* Header */}
    <div class="mb-8 relative">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-4 px-8 rounded-lg relative">
        {/* Primary accent left */}
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-4 h-full bg-[#25D007] rounded-l-lg"></div>
        {/* Primary accent right */}
        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-4 h-full bg-[#25D007] rounded-r-lg"></div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center relative z-10">
          I8 Fun Referral Program: Earn by Inviting Friends
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Main Content */}
    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Discover the exciting referral program in I8 Fun, a popular gaming platform designed for Pakistani players. This feature lets you invite friends and family to join the fun, playing casino-style games like Aviator, Mines, and slots to earn real money. It's a simple way to boost your earnings without extra effort.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">What is the Referral Program?</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The referral program rewards you for bringing new players to I8 Fun. Share your unique link, and when your referrals sign up and start playing, you earn bonuses. It's a community-driven way to maximize your income from the app's engaging games.
      </p>

      <div class="my-8 flex justify-center">
        <div class="w-full max-w-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <Image
            src={referralImage}
            alt="I8 Fun Referral Program Illustration"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            width={600}
            height={600}
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">How Does It Work?</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Getting started is easy. Follow these steps to begin earning through referrals:
      </p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Log in to your I8 Fun account and find your referral link in the profile or rewards section.</li>
        <li>Share the link with friends, family, or acquaintances via social media, messaging apps, or direct invites.</li>
        <li>Once they download the app, register, and make their first deposit, your referral is activated.</li>
        <li>Earn a bonus for each successful referral who meets the minimum deposit and betting requirements.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        For example, when a referred player deposits at least 500 PKR and places bets totaling 5,000 PKR, you receive a 600 PKR reward. Invite more players to unlock higher tiers, like special bonuses for reaching 10 referrals.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Benefits of Joining the Referral Program</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Passive income: Earn without playing extra games yourself.</li>
        <li>Flexible rewards: Bonuses are added directly to your wallet for easy withdrawals via JazzCash or Easypaisa.</li>
        <li>Community growth: Help others enjoy I8 Fun while building your network.</li>
        <li>No upfront costs: Start sharing links right away after registering.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Tips for Success</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To maximize your referrals, focus on genuine invites. Encourage new players to explore games like Fortune Gems or Lucky Wheel. Track your progress in the app and stay updated on promotions for extra incentives.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Conclusion</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        The I8 Fun referral program is an ideal opportunity for Pakistani gamers to earn more by expanding their circle. It's straightforward, rewarding, and complements the app's thrilling games. Download I8 Fun today, grab your referral link, and start inviting friends to share in the excitement and earnings!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
